outputs.output_descr: The SPSP project will work with all MPs from the Government and the Opposition to strengthen their capacity to use parliamentary processes to more effectively engage with national developmeent issues. Accordingly, this project aims to work with (1) MPs directly (Output 1 & 2) and (2) the Parliamentary Secretariat (Outputs 2-4) to strengthen the capacity of Samoa's MPs to more effectively & accountability promote & progress Samoa's national development priorities & the achievement of the MDGs.

project_descr: Buildding capacity for Samoa Parliamentarians for Good Governance
